Distribution. Western Atlantic— USA ( North Carolina , South Carolina , Georgia , Florida, Mississippi , Louisiana , Texas ), Gulf of Mexico , Mexico , Bahamas , Belize , Panama , Cuba , Jamaica , Puerto Rico , Virgin Islands , Antigua , Barbados , Colombia , Venezuela , Guyana , Suriname , French Guiana , Brazil ( Amapá , Pará, Ceará , Rio Grande do Norte , Paraíba , Pernambuco , Alagoas , Sergipe , Bahia , Espírito Santo , Rio de Janeiro , São Paulo , Paraná , Santa Catarina, Rio Grande do Sul ), Uruguay ( Werding 1982 ; Coelho-Santos & Coelho 1994 ; Melo 1999 ;
